<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>写程序的龙龙 (Posts about Linux)</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/categories/cat_linux.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2018 13:28:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>测试时，Docker终端无法显示中文</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ce-shi-shi-dockerzhong-duan-wu-fa-xian-shi-zhong-wen/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;测试代码的时候，无法用print在Docker终端输出中文，对于这个问题，我们采用的办法是将要输出的信息记录在redis里，然后在主系统通过redis图形客户端查看，这样的好处在于:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol class="arabic simple"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;不需要改动docker镜像本身；&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;redis可以很好地支持中文；&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;测试过程可记录，容易追溯问题所在。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>Docker</category><category>redis</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ce-shi-shi-dockerzhong-duan-wu-fa-xian-shi-zhong-wen/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 30 Dec 2017 16:00:02 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Redis修改默认端口</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/redisxiu-gai-mo-ren-duan-kou/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;pre class="literal-block"&gt;
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; emacs /etc/redis/redis.conf
port 8083
bind 0.0.0.0
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; redis-server /etc/redis/redis.conf
&lt;/pre&gt;</description><category>redis</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/redisxiu-gai-mo-ren-duan-kou/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 30 Dec 2017 15:31:05 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>使用Tmux实现终端分屏</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/shi-yong-tmuxshi-xian-zhong-duan-fen-ping/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;在终端下工作时，经常要打开多个窗口，运用Tmux就可以只开一个终端，分屏进行操作了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;首先按下Ctrl-b，然后按下对应按键完成功能：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table border="1" class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;colgroup&gt;
&lt;col width="19%"&gt;
&lt;col width="81%"&gt;
&lt;/colgroup&gt;
&lt;thead valign="bottom"&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;th class="head"&gt;按键&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th class="head"&gt;功能&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/thead&gt;
&lt;tbody valign="top"&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;s&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;列出所有会话&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;$&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;重命名当前会话&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;d&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;断开当前会话&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;c&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;创建一个新窗口&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;,&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;重命名当前窗口&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;w&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;列出所有窗口&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;%&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;水平分割窗口&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;"&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;竖直分割窗口&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;n&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;下一个窗口&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;p&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;上一个窗口&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;0~9&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;选择对应的窗口&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;q&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;显示窗格的编号&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;l&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;与上一个窗口循环切换&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;o&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;在窗格之间切换&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;}&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;与下一个窗格交换位置&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;{&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;与上一个窗格交换位置&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;!&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;在新窗口中显示当前窗格&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;x&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;关闭当前窗格&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;t&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;显示当前时间&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>Tmux</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/shi-yong-tmuxshi-xian-zhong-duan-fen-ping/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 30 Dec 2017 07:36:55 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Ubuntu命令行连接wifi</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ubuntuming-ling-xing-lian-jie-wifi/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;pre class="literal-block"&gt;
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; cd /usr/local/bin/
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; cd /home/long
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; wpa_passphrase SSID PWD &amp;gt; /home/long/wifi.conf
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; sudo emacs /etc/network/interfaces
auto wlan0
iface wlan0 inet dhcp
wpa-conf /home/long/wifi.conf
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; sudo reboot
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;注意&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;路由器必须要打开DHCP才可以正常连接。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>Ubuntu</category><category>wifi</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ubuntuming-ling-xing-lian-jie-wifi/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jul 2017 03:06:54 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>基于mqtt的json格式消息推送</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;基于文章 &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-xiao-xi-tui-song/"&gt;https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-xiao-xi-tui-song/&lt;/a&gt; ，我们进一步改进测试程序。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;t2上&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;编写并启动消息接收端。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;table class="codetable"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos"&gt;&lt;div class="linenodiv"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-1"&gt; 1&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-2"&gt; 2&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-3"&gt; 3&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-4"&gt; 4&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-5"&gt; 5&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-6"&gt; 6&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-7"&gt; 7&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-8"&gt; 8&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-9"&gt; 9&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-10"&gt;10&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-11"&gt;11&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-12"&gt;12&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-13"&gt;13&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-14"&gt;14&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-15"&gt;15&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-16"&gt;16&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-17"&gt;17&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-18"&gt;18&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-19"&gt;19&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-20"&gt;20&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;pre class="code python"&gt;&lt;a name="rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="kn"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nn"&gt;paho.mqtt.client&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="kn"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nn"&gt;mqtt&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-2"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="kn"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nn"&gt;json&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-3"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-4"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nf"&gt;on_connect&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;client&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;userdata&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;flags&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;rc&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;):&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-5"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;span class="n"&gt;client&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;subscribe&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"test"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-6"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-7"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nf"&gt;on_message&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;client&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;userdata&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;msg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;):&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-8"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;span class="k"&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;msg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;topic&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;" "&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nb"&gt;str&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;msg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;payload&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;))&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-9"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;span class="n"&gt;message&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;json&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;loads&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;msg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;payload&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;decode&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"utf-8"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;))&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-10"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;span class="k"&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;message&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"1"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;])&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-11"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;span class="k"&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;message&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"2"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;])&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-12"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-13"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;client&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;mqtt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;Client&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-14"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;client&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;on_connect&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;on_connect&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-15"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;client&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;on_message&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;on_message&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-16"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-17"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;span class="n"&gt;client&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;connect&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"172.16.0.111"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;port&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;1883&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-18"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;span class="n"&gt;client&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;loop_forever&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-19"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;except&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="ne"&gt;KeyboardInterrupt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_381e2d91a0034144ad1e1b673c3ba084-20"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;span class="n"&gt;client&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;disconnect&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;t3上&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;编写并启动消息发送端。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;table class="codetable"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos"&gt;&lt;div class="linenodiv"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_4da207db62e84eb88aff51a913ea2130-1"&gt; 1&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_4da207db62e84eb88aff51a913ea2130-2"&gt; 2&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_4da207db62e84eb88aff51a913ea2130-3"&gt; 3&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_4da207db62e84eb88aff51a913ea2130-4"&gt; 4&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ji-yu-mqttde-jsonge-shi-xiao-xi-tui-song/#rest_code_4da207db62e84eb88aff51a913ea2130-5"&gt; 5&lt;/a&gt;
